description: Firebase config from env vars only — no hardcoded values
globs: src/firebase.js, src/AppContext.jsx
alwaysApply: false
---

# Firebase

- **Config source:** `import.meta.env.VITE_FIREBASE_*` only — never hardcode API keys or project IDs
- **`.env.example`:** Documents required vars; copy to `.env` and fill
- **Graceful fallback:** When env vars are missing, `auth` and `db` are null; app runs in UI-only mode
- **AppContext:** Checks `auth` / `db` before use; `sendMagicLink` throws if Firebase not configured
